reviewText: As far as I can tell, this is an extremely low *LOW* quality video of hand held photos probably shot at someones kitchen table.  The photos are blurry and unclear.  The commentary does not give you any clue at all as to what you are supposed to be looking at.  No background story or meaningful commentary is offered at all.  Comments are along the lines of "maybe we should have close encounters music".  What are we supposed to be seeing?  What is the story?
